Resource Profile: Road Safety Encounter

Official URL: https://build.fhir.org/ig/UPM-NTHC/PH-RoadSafetyIG/StructureDefinition/rs-encounter Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-10-16 Computable Name: RSEncounter

Encounter for EMS run report / facility submission context. Captures incident number, type, timing, participants, disposition & transfer.

Usages:

  • Use this Profile: Road Safety Bundle — EMS Submission and Road Safety Bundle — ONEISS Submission
  • Refer to this Profile: Road Safety Condition, Road Safety DocumentReference (Evidence), Road Safety Observation, Road Safety Procedure and Road Safety ServiceRequest

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
